data.description: This freshly updated 3-beds, 2-bath home is ready to welcome you with open arms & features numerous brand new upgrades, like stainless steel kitchen appliances, new interior paint & flooring, & newly installed countertops throughout. The home’s spacious & thoughtful layout is characterized by an open & inviting common area & also with bedrooms that are generously sized enough to ensure comfort & privacy for everyone in the home. And the master suite is a true retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom & walk-in closet, it’s the perfect sanctuary to relax & unwind. The property also has a 3-car garage & a bonus room that could be used as an office, den, or for extra storage. Outside features a large & well-maintained yard with no rear neighbors presenting endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gatherings, or even to create your own garden oasis, with a covered patio that’s the perfect place to take in your very own beautiful Idaho view-it’s quiet, secluded, & close to everywhere you want to be.
